                        & TRIM(NumberToVString(VARIABLE_TYPE,"*",ERR,ERROR))//" of field number "// &
                        & TRIM(NumberToVString(FIELD%USER_NUMBER,"*",ERR,ERROR))//" which has Gauss point based interpolation."
